data.description: DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS CUTIE WITH ENDLESS VIEWS!!  Sweet ranch home on 6.86 acres in the desirable Catheys Valley community is NOW AVAILABLE!!!!    ELECTRIC FENCING SURROUNDS THE ENTIRE PROPERTY AND POWERED BY A SOLAR PANEL. Cross fenced as well and a SOLAR POWERED gated entrance secures plenty of room for your favorite livestock!    A GENERAC GENERATOR WITH ITS OWN SEPARATE 250 GALLON PROPANE TANK ALONG WITH ROOF SPRINKLERS FOR FIRE PROTECTION are just a few of the "STAND OUTS" offered!!    Nicely UPDATED 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom,  900 Sq. Ft. with beautiful wood flooring, granite countertops, handsomely appointed wood burning fireplace PLUS...an easterly facing front porch makes this setting a STAR!!! OFFERING A CARPORT AND ADDITIONAL STORAGE ROOM AS WELL.    FRUIT TREES ON YOUR LIST??  Apricot, Pear, Orange, Nectarines, Fig and Pomegranate trees with sprinklers on a timer system that waters the trees in addition to the front and backyard! EXCELLENT WATER AREA PER OWNER!!!    UNDERGROUND WATER LINE TO THE UPPER BARN WITH COVERED STALLS FOR ANIMALS CARE AND PROTECTION PLUS A NEW 364 Sq. FT. BARN STYLE STORAGE BUILDING!  THE RANCH SETTING ALSO INCLUDES AN ESTABLISHED CHICKEN COOP AND GARDEN AREA FOR YOUR GREEN THUMB!!!!    SEEMINGLY ALWAYS A BREEZE AT THIS MIGHTY OASIS IN THE HEART OF THE SIERRA FOOTHILLS OF MARIPOSA COUNTY AND VERY NEAR THE WONDERFUL CATHEYS VALLEY CHARTER SCHOOL!!!    24 HOUR NOTICE TO SHOW.....
